Invocation Name: my energy
Developer Terms of Use
des:
Okaya is your wellbeing companion. We help you track your energy levels and put you in touch with the right wellbeing professionals for you.

When you give us some simple information about yourself we can help you feel more energized, manage fatigue, and avoid burnout.

Alexa skill and Okaya app are compatible and the information and data can be checked using either services

Disclaimer: Please remember that Okaya does not provide medical advice, and is for informational and educational purposes only, and is not a substitute for professional medical advice, treatment or diagnosis. Call your doctor to receive medical advice. If you think you may have a medical emergency, please dial your local emergency response phone number.
